cs.IR, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.MM 

This paper is about large-scale search and retrieval of information, which is a common problem in information retrieval (IR) and computer vision (CV). The paper discusses different approaches for efficient search, which are relevant to machine learning (ML) and data mining (DB) as well. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR, followed by cs.CV and cs.LG. cs.DB and cs.MM are also possible sub-categories since they deal with data management and multimedia, respectively, which are relevant to the problem of large-scale retrieval.
